# These settings can also go under an "Account" section, but then the
# "IMAPStore" section needs to reference the account. This is not
# needed for just one store per account.
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
Sync All

IMAPAccount posteo
Host posteo.de
User mail
#PassCmd "bw get password d1d6018d-92fc-4011-816a-ac0200ddd77e"
PassCmd "pass email/posteo"
SSLType STARTTLS

IMAPStore posteo-remote
Account posteo

MaildirStore posteo-local
Path ~/.mail/posteo/
Inbox ~/.mail/posteo/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel posteo
Far :posteo-remote:
Near :posteo-local:
Patterns * !Archives

IMAPAccount uni
Host exchange.uni.de
User nickname
#PassCmd "bw get password d1d6018d-92fc-4011-816a-ac0200ddd77e"
PassCmd "pass email/uni"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersion TLSv1.2
AuthMechs PLAIN
Timeout 120
PipelineDepth 50

IMAPStore uni-remote
Account uni

MaildirStore uni-local
Path ~/.mail/uni/
Inbox ~/.mail/uni/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel uni
Far :uni-remote:
Near :uni-local:
Patterns * !Archives
